item.title: About
item.description: Somewhere in Kyoto, 2019 Welcome to my little corner on the Internet. Like this space, I am a work in progress. I am currently based in India, and I find joy in getting computers to do fun, and mostly useful things. A recent accomplishment I am most proud of involves riding a bicycle for three hours around Lyon, France in April 2022, when I had only learned to ride it the previous year.
